name: 🌸👗 Women's Clothing and Book Swap! 👗🌸
description:
Join us at our Women's Clothing and Book Swap event! Bring your gently-used clothing and books to trade, swap, and discover new favorites. It's a fantastic opportunity to refresh your style and expand your reading collection, all while connecting with other women in the community.

🌷 How it works:

1️⃣ Bring a minimum of one clothing item or book to participate.

2️⃣ Trade with others or give away your items!

See you there! 👋
